<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Abstract</h2>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Academic institutions face major challenges in unifying student progress markers such as attendance sheets, course marks, schedules, announcements, and assignment workflows. Legacy administrative software often splits these datasets, preventing students from obtaining a complete view of their placement readiness.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">This project report describes the design and development of <strong>AcadTrack</strong>, a centralized, web-based Student Academic Journey Tracker built on the <strong>MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js)</strong> stack. AcadTrack introduces a secure, role-based architecture for Administrators, Faculty, and Students. Security is enhanced through a two-step authentication system featuring One-Time Passwords (OTP) delivered via the Brevo HTTPS REST API, alongside bcryptjs password encryption and JSON Web Tokens (JWT) for stateless session management.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Key features include:</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Placement Eligibility Evaluator:</strong> Computes eligibility in real-time based on cumulative GPA, attendance rates, and backlog counts.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>Visual Timetable Scheduler:</strong> Supports class slot management with conflict detection.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Assignment and Grading Module:</strong> Streamlines course evaluations, attendance registry tracking, and role-based announcement boards.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Testing results verify that the system successfully prevents timing overlap errors in classrooms, restricts unauthorized access through custom middleware, and scales efficiently under simulated database environments.</p>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

