<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 1: Introduction</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.1 Project Overview</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The management of student academic data in higher education involves multiple stakeholders, including administrators, faculty, and students. Historically, these groups have interacted with disconnected tools. <strong>AcadTrack</strong> is an integrated web platform designed to combine grade tracking, attendance monitoring, scheduling, and notifications into a single interface.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">By building the system on the <strong>MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js)</strong> stack, AcadTrack leverages a unified codebase to deliver dynamic analytics. The goal of AcadTrack is to simplify record-keeping and improve communication between faculty and students.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.2 Purpose and Objectives</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The main objectives of AcadTrack are:</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Consolidate Academic Records:</strong> Create a single database for users, courses, grades, attendance, notices, and assignments.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>Enable Placement Tracking:</strong> Develop an automated evaluator that calculates a student's eligibility for recruitment drives based on GPA, attendance, and backlogs.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Provide Conflict-Free Scheduling:</strong> Include a scheduling module that prevents room booking conflicts.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">4.  <strong>Strengthen Security:</strong> Implement secure authentication using hashed passwords, session tokens, and email-based OTP verification.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.3 Scope of the System</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The system is designed to support three user roles:</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Students:</strong> Can view their GPA trends, course attendance, upcoming assignments, and placement eligibility.</li>
<li>  <strong>Faculty:</strong> Can take attendance, submit grades, post assignments, and publish notices.</li>
<li>  <strong>Administrators:</strong> Can manage user accounts, assign faculty to courses, and configure global academic settings.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.4 Document Organization</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">This report is divided into ten chapters. <strong>Chapter 2</strong> evaluates the technical stack and existing software limits. <strong>Chapter 3</strong> defines the system requirements. <strong>Chapter 4</strong> outlines UML models and DFD flow charts. <strong>Chapter 5</strong> presents the database data dictionary. <strong>Chapter 6</strong> details the core implementation. <strong>Chapter 7</strong> highlights security policies. <strong>Chapter 8</strong> details the QA test suite, and <strong>Chapters 9 and 10</strong> outline future enhancements and conclusions.</p>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 2: System Analysis &amp; Feasibility Study</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.1 MERN Stack Architecture</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The MERN stack uses JavaScript across the entire application:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">[Client Tier: React]  &lt;==== JSON via HTTP ====&gt;  [App Tier: Express/Node] &lt;==== Mongoose ====&gt; [DB Tier: MongoDB]</p>
</code></pre>

<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>React:</strong> Renders the user interface. It updates components based on state changes to maintain a responsive dashboard.</li>
<li>  <strong>Node.js &amp; Express:</strong> Serve as the application server, handling routes, middleware, and database connections.</li>
<li>  <strong>MongoDB:</strong> Stores data in BSON format, providing a flexible document schema suitable for handling varied academic records.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.2 Existing System Pitfalls</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Legacy systems often suffer from:</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Data Fragmentation:</strong> Grade data, attendance sheets, and assignment submissions are frequently kept in separate files or tools, requiring manual reconciliation.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>Delayed Alerts:</strong> Students may not receive timely warnings if their attendance or GPA falls below eligibility thresholds.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Vulnerability to Tampering:</strong> Simple client-side checks and basic authentication make records vulnerable to unauthorized changes.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">4.  <strong>Scheduling Conflicts:</strong> Manual timetabling often leads to double-booking of classrooms or instructors.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.3 Proposed System Advantages</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack addresses these challenges by:</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Unifying Data:</strong> Managing all information in a central database to ensure consistency.</li>
<li>  <strong>Automating Eligibility Checks:</strong> Calculating placement eligibility dynamically to help students track their status.</li>
<li>  <strong>Preventing Room Conflicts:</strong> Validating schedule entries on the server to block overlapping bookings.</li>
<li>  <strong>Securing Access:</strong> Using email OTPs and JWT tokens to verify user identities and authorize requests.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.4 Feasibility Study</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.4.1 Technical Feasibility</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Mongoose ODM</strong> simplifies queries and enforces document structures within MongoDB.</li>
<li>  <strong>Brevo HTTPS API</strong> manages email verification to ensure reliable delivery of OTP codes.</li>
<li>  <strong>Vite</strong> bundles frontend assets, optimizing rendering speeds for the client application.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.4.2 Economic Feasibility</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack is built on open-source technologies, avoiding licensing costs. The system can be deployed on standard cloud infrastructure, minimizing setup and maintenance expenses.</p>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.4.3 Operational Feasibility</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The application features distinct layouts tailored to each role, simplifying workflows for students, faculty, and administrators. This reduces the need for extensive training.</p>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 3: Software Requirements Specification (SRS)</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.1 General Description</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack provides tools to manage academic activities, track student performance, and coordinate schedules. The system is designed to run in modern web browsers, connecting securely to the backend API.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.2 User Roles</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Administrator:</strong> Sets up courses, manages user profiles, and monitors overall system statistics.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>Faculty:</strong> Manages attendance sheets, records grades, posts assignments, and reviews student submissions.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Student:</strong> Accesses grades, checks attendance percentages, submits assignments, and reviews notices.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3 Functional Requirements</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3.1 Authentication &amp; Security (FR-01)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Registration:</strong> Users must provide a name, email, password, role, department, and ID.</li>
<li>  <strong>OTP Verification:</strong> Before granting a session, the system must send a 6-digit OTP to the user's email, which must be verified within 5 minutes.</li>
<li>  <strong>Session Management:</strong> Authorized users are issued a JWT to authenticate subsequent requests.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3.2 Student Progress Dashboard (FR-02)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Key Metrics:</strong> Display GPA, earned credits, overall attendance, and backlog counts.</li>
<li>  <strong>GPA Visualization:</strong> Render an interactive trend line showing SGPA and CGPA changes over semesters.</li>
<li>  <strong>Placement Checker:</strong> Display eligibility status using the criteria: CGPA <span style="font-style:italic;">\ge</span> 7.0, Attendance <span style="font-style:italic;">\ge</span> 75%, and 0 backlogs.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3.3 Timetable and Schedule Planner (FR-03)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Display:</strong> Render a weekly grid showing schedule details (course, time, classroom, instructor).</li>
<li>  <strong>Conflict Prevention:</strong> Check schedule entries on the server to prevent double-booking of classrooms on the same day and time.</li>
<li>  <strong>Role Views:</strong> Customize views (students see their classes, faculty see their teaching hours, admins view all slots).</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3.4 Lecture Attendance Tracker (FR-04)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Recording:</strong> Allow faculty to mark students as <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">Present</code> or <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">Absent</code> for a specific course and date.</li>
<li>  <strong>Uniqueness:</strong> Restrict attendance records to one entry per course per day.</li>
<li>  <strong>Aggregation:</strong> Calculate overall and subject-specific attendance percentages.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3.5 Assignment &amp; Grading Portal (FR-05)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Creation:</strong> Allow faculty to post assignments with descriptions and reference documents.</li>
<li>  <strong>Submission:</strong> Allow students to upload PDF files for assignments before the due date.</li>
<li>  <strong>Grading:</strong> Provide a interface for faculty to grade submissions and leave feedback.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3.6 Announcement Notice Board (FR-06)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Creation:</strong> Allow admins and faculty to write and publish notices.</li>
<li>  <strong>Targeting:</strong> Filter notices based on the intended audience (e.g., student or faculty).</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.4 Non-Functional Requirements</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.4.1 Security &amp; Access Controls (NFR-01)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Encrypt all passwords using <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">bcryptjs</code>.</li>
<li>  Validate requests on the server using JWT signature checks.</li>
<li>  Restrict API routes using role-based authorization rules.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.4.2 Performance &amp; Latency (NFR-02)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Ensure backend API response times remain under 200ms.</li>
<li>  Optimize database queries using targeted indexes.</li>
<li>  Load frontend components efficiently by caching assets on the client.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.4.3 Reliability &amp; Database Constraints (NFR-03)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Enforce schema constraints and unique indexes to prevent duplicate entries.</li>
<li>  Manage transaction status to ensure data consistency during updates.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.4.4 Usability &amp; Responsiveness (NFR-04)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Implement a responsive web interface using Tailwind CSS.</li>
<li>  Support modern web browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge).</li>
</ul>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.5 Hardware and Software Specifications</h3>

<table style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; margin:12pt 0; border:1px solid #000;"><tr style="background-color:#f8fafc;"><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Component</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Minimum Specification</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Recommended Specification</th></tr>

<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Server OS</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Ubuntu Linux 20.04 LTS</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Ubuntu Linux 22.04 LTS</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Database</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">MongoDB 6.0</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">MongoDB Atlas (Cloud Cluster)</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Node.js</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">v18.x</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">v20.x</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Server RAM</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">2 GB</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">4 GB or more</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Client CPU</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Intel Core i5 / AMD Ryzen 5</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Client RAM</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">4 GB</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">8 GB</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Web Browser</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Chrome 100+ / Firefox 95+</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Chrome Latest / Safari Latest</td></tr>
</table>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 4: System Design &amp; UML Modeling</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.1 System Architecture Diagram</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack uses a decoupled, three-tier architecture:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">graph TD</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">subgraph UI_Tier [Client Tier (React)]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">App[React Application]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Router[React Router DOM]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Recharts[Recharts Engines]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthContext[Auth Context State]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">end</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">subgraph App_Tier [Application Tier (Node/Express)]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Express[Express Web Framework]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthGuard[JWT Auth Guard Middleware]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">UploadGuard[Multer File Filter Middleware]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Controllers[API Controllers]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">end</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">subgraph Service_Tier [Integration Services]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Brevo[Brevo REST API]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">end</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">subgraph DB_Tier [Database Tier (MongoDB)]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">MongoDB[(MongoDB Database)]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">end</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">App &lt;==&gt;|HTTPS JSON Request| Express</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Express --&gt; AuthGuard</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Express --&gt; UploadGuard</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthGuard --&gt; Controllers</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">UploadGuard --&gt; Controllers</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Controllers &lt;==&gt;|Mongoose Queries| MongoDB</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Controllers --&gt;|Email Delivery HTTP POST| Brevo</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2 UML Diagrams</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.1 Use Case Diagram</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">This diagram shows the actions available to each user role:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">leftToRightDirection</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">fc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">actor Admin as "System Administrator"</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">actor Faculty as "Faculty Member"</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">actor Student as "Enrolled Student"</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">rectangle "AcadTrack Platform" {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Manage User Profiles" as UC_Admin_Users</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Manage Course Allocations" as UC_Admin_Courses</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Create Schedule Slots" as UC_Sched_Create</p>
        
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Mark Course Attendance" as UC_Fac_Att</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Post Assignment Briefs" as UC_Fac_Assign</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Grade Submissions" as UC_Fac_Grades</p>
        
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Submit Assignments" as UC_Stu_Sub</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "Check Academic Dashboard" as UC_Stu_Dash</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">usecase "View Notice Board" as UC_Notices</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">end</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Admin --&gt; UC_Admin_Users</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Admin --&gt; UC_Admin_Courses</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Admin --&gt; UC_Sched_Create</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Faculty --&gt; UC_Fac_Att</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Faculty --&gt; UC_Fac_Assign</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Faculty --&gt; UC_Fac_Grades</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Faculty --&gt; UC_Sched_Create</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Student --&gt; UC_Stu_Sub</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Student --&gt; UC_Stu_Dash</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Student --&gt; UC_Notices</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.2 Data Flow Diagram (DFD Level 1)</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Shows the flow of information between users, processes, and the database:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">graph TD</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User([User])</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc[1.0 Session Auth &amp; OTP]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CourseProc[2.0 Course &amp; Enrollment]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">GradingProc[3.0 Grading &amp; GPA Calculations]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AttendProc[4.0 Attendance Tracker]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SchedProc[5.0 Schedule Management]</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">DB[(MongoDB Database)]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Mailer[Brevo Mailer]</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Login Credentials| AuthProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc --&gt;|Send OTP Code| Mailer</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc &lt;==&gt;|Verify &amp; Query Session| DB</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc --&gt;|JWT Token| User</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Manage Course/User| CourseProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CourseProc &lt;==&gt;|Write Course Details| DB</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Grade Marks| GradingProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">GradingProc &lt;==&gt;|Update AcademicRecord| DB</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Submit Attendance Sheet| AttendProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AttendProc &lt;==&gt;|Write Attendance| DB</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Create Timetable Slot| SchedProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SchedProc &lt;==&gt;|Write Schedule Slot| DB</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.3 Entity-Relationship Diagram (ERD)</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Defines the relationships between data entities:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">erDiagram</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string name</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string email UK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string password</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string role</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string studentId</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string facultyId</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string department</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number semester</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Course {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string name</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string code UK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number credits</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string department</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId faculty FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcademicRecord {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId student FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number semester</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">array courses</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number sgpa</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number cgpa</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Attendance {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId course FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">date date</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">array records</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Assignment {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string title</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string description</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId course FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">date dueDate</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string fileUrl</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Submission {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId assignment FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId student FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string fileUrl</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">date submittedAt</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string grade</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string feedback</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string status</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Schedule {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId course FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string dayOfWeek</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string startTime</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string endTime</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string classroom</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User ||--o{ Course : teaches_or_enrolled</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User ||--o{ AcademicRecord : owns</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Course ||--o{ Attendance : tracks</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Course ||--o{ Assignment : contains</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Assignment ||--o{ Submission : has</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User ||--o{ Submission : submits</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Course ||--o{ Schedule : runs_on</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.4 Activity Diagram: Placement Eligibility Engine</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Describes the logic used to determine recruitment eligibility:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">flowchart TD</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Start([Start Evaluation]) --&gt; FetchData[Fetch Student Profile &amp; Academic History]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">FetchData --&gt; CheckCGPA{Is CGPA &gt;= 7.0?}</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckCGPA -- No --&gt; SetIneligible[Set Eligible = False]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckCGPA -- Yes --&gt; FetchAttendance[Calculate Overall Attendance Percentage]</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">FetchAttendance --&gt; CheckAtt{Is Attendance &gt;= 75%?}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckAtt -- No --&gt; SetIneligible</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckAtt -- Yes --&gt; FetchGrades[Scan Records for Grade F]</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">FetchGrades --&gt; CheckBacklogs{Any Backlogs Found?}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckBacklogs -- Yes --&gt; SetIneligible</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckBacklogs -- No --&gt; SetEligible[Set Eligible = True]</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SetIneligible --&gt; OutputResult[Return Status and Criteria Metrics]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SetEligible --&gt; OutputResult</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">OutputResult --&gt; End([End Evaluation])</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 5: Database Design &amp; Data Dictionary</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.1 MongoDB Document Modeling</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack uses MongoDB schemas designed to maintain references while avoiding deep nesting. This approach balances read performance with update efficiency.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.2 Data Dictionary Tables</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Table 5.1: Users Collection (<code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">users</code>)</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Stores profile information for all system users:</p>

<table style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; margin:12pt 0; border:1px solid #000;"><tr style="background-color:#f8fafc;"><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Field Name</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Data Type</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Key Type</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Nullable</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Description / Constraints</th></tr>

<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">_id</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">ObjectId</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">PK</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Unique auto-generated identifier</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">name</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">String</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">-</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Full name of the user</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">email</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">String</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">UK</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Institutional email (unique, lowercase)</td></tr>
