<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Stores timetable slot allocations:</p>

<table style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; margin:12pt 0; border:1px solid #000;"><tr style="background-color:#f8fafc;"><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Field Name</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Data Type</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Key Type</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Nullable</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Description / Constraints</th></tr>

<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">_id</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">ObjectId</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">PK</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Unique identifier</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">course</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">ObjectId</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">FK</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">References <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">Course._id</code></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">dayOfWeek</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">String</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">-</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Enum: <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">['Monday', 'Tuesday', ..., 'Sunday']</code></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">startTime</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">String</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">-</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Lecture start time (HH:MM)</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">endTime</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">String</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">-</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Lecture end time (HH:MM)</td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">classroom</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">String</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">-</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">No</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Assigned room identifier</td></tr>
</table>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.3 Indexing and Uniqueness Constraints</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Users:</strong> Unique index on <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">email</code>. Sparse unique indexes on <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">studentId</code> and <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">facultyId</code> allow these fields to be optional for admins while enforcing uniqueness for other roles.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>Academic Records:</strong> Compound unique index on <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">{ student: 1, semester: 1 }</code> prevents duplicate semester records for a student.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Attendance:</strong> Compound unique index on <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">{ course: 1, date: 1 }</code> restricts attendance entry to once per course per day.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">4.  <strong>Submissions:</strong> Compound unique index on <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">{ assignment: 1, student: 1 }</code> limits students to one file upload per assignment.</p>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 6: System Implementation Details</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">6.1 Backend Server Entry Point</h3>
<code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">backend/server.js</code> initializes the Express application, sets up middleware, and connects to MongoDB:

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import express from 'express';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import dotenv from 'dotenv';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import cors from 'cors';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import path from 'path';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import connectDB from './config/db.js';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import authRoutes from './routes/authRoutes.js';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import scheduleRoutes from './routes/scheduleRoutes.js';</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">dotenv.config();</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">connectDB();</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const app = express();</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">app.use(cors({ origin: process.env.FRONTEND_URL || '*', credentials: true }));</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">app.use(express.json());</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">// Serving Uploads</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">app.use('/uploads', express.static(path.join(path.resolve(), 'uploads')));</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">// Routes</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">app.use('/api/auth', authRoutes);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">app.use('/api/schedule', scheduleRoutes);</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const PORT = process.env.PORT || 5000;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">app.listen(PORT, () =&gt; console.log(<code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">Server started on port <span style="font-style:italic;">{PORT}</code>));</p>
</code></pre>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">6.2 Two-Step Verification (OTP Module)</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Authentication requires email verification. The code below from [mailer.js](file:///d:/college-lms/backend/config/mailer.js) sends the OTP code using the Brevo API:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const sendOTPEmail = async (email, name, otp, purpose) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (!process.env.BREVO_SMTP_KEY) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">console.log(<code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">[TEST MODE] OTP: </span>{otp}</code>);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return true;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const response = await fetch('https://api.brevo.com/v3/smtp/email', {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">method: 'POST',</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">headers: {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">'accept': 'application/json',</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">'api-key': process.env.BREVO_SMTP_KEY,</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">'content-type': 'application/json',</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">},</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">body: JSON.stringify({</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">sender: { name: 'AcadTrack Admin', email: process.env.BREVO_SENDER_EMAIL },</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">to: [{ email, name }],</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">subject: 'Verification Code',</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">htmlContent: <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">&lt;p&gt;Your verification code is &lt;strong&gt;<span style="font-style:italic;">{otp}&lt;/strong&gt; for </span>{purpose}.&lt;/p&gt;</code>,</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}),</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return response.ok;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>
</code></pre>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">6.3 Placement Engine Calculation Mechanics</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The placement eligibility engine computes status flags on demand in the dashboard controller:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">export const getStudentDashboardStats = async (req, res) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const studentId = req.user._id;</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const records = await AcademicRecord.find({ student: studentId }).sort({ semester: 1 });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const cgpa = records.length &gt; 0 ? records[records.length - 1].cgpa : 0.0;</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">let backlogs = 0;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">records.forEach(rec =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">rec.courses.forEach(c =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (c.grade === 'F') backlogs++;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const enrolledCourses = await Course.find({ studentsEnrolled: studentId });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">let totalClasses = 0, presents = 0;</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">for (let course of enrolledCourses) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const atts = await Attendance.find({ course: course._id });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">atts.forEach(att =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const match = att.records.find(r =&gt; r.student.toString() === studentId.toString());</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (match) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">totalClasses++;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (match.status === 'Present') presents++;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const overallAttendance = totalClasses &gt; 0 ? (presents / totalClasses) * 100 : 100;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const eligible = cgpa &gt;= 7.0 &amp;&amp; overallAttendance &gt;= 75.0 &amp;&amp; backlogs === 0;</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">res.json({</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">summary: { cgpa, overallAttendance, backlogCount: backlogs },</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">eligibleStatus: eligible</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>
</code></pre>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">6.4 Classroom Schedule Conflict Detection</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The schedule manager verifies booking slots to prevent room double-booking:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">export const createSchedule = async (req, res) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const { course, dayOfWeek, startTime, endTime, classroom } = req.body;</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (startTime &gt;= endTime) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return res.status(400).json({ message: 'Start time must precede end time.' });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">// Conflict Check: Classroom, Day, Overlapping Time</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const conflicts = await Schedule.find({ dayOfWeek, classroom });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const hasConflict = conflicts.some(slot =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return (</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">(startTime &gt;= slot.startTime &amp;&amp; startTime &lt; slot.endTime) ||</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">(endTime &gt; slot.startTime &amp;&amp; endTime &lt;= slot.endTime) ||</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">(startTime &lt;= slot.startTime &amp;&amp; endTime &gt;= slot.endTime)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (hasConflict) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return res.status(400).json({ message: 'Room conflict detected for the selected time slot.' });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const newSlot = await Schedule.create({ course, dayOfWeek, startTime, endTime, classroom });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">res.status(201).json(newSlot);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>
</code></pre>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">6.5 Frontend Navigation and Routing</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The application uses React Router DOM to manage access to routes based on user roles:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import React, { useContext } from 'react';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import { Navigate } from 'react-router-dom';</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">import { AuthContext } from '../context/AuthContext';</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const ProtectedRoute = ({ children, allowedRoles }) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const { user, loading } = useContext(AuthContext);</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (loading) return &lt;div&gt;Loading Session...&lt;/div&gt;;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (!user) return &lt;Navigate to="/login" replace /&gt;;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (allowedRoles &amp;&amp; !allowedRoles.includes(user.role)) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return &lt;Navigate to="/login" replace /&gt;;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return children;</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">export default ProtectedRoute;</p>
</code></pre>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 7: Security Engineering &amp; Integrity Protection</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">7.1 Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) Middleware</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The backend validates user tokens and roles before routing API requests:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">export const protect = async (req, res, next) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">let token = req.headers.authorization?.split(' ')[1];</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (!token) return res.status(401).json({ message: 'Access Denied: No Token' });</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">try {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const decoded = jwt.verify(token, process.env.JWT_SECRET);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">req.user = await User.findById(decoded.id).select('-password');</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">next();</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">} catch (err) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">res.status(401).json({ message: 'Access Denied: Invalid Token' });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">export const authorize = (...roles) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return (req, res, next) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (!roles.includes(req.user.role)) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return res.status(403).json({ message: 'Access Denied: Unauthorized Role' });</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">next();</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>
</code></pre>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">7.2 Password Cryptography and Salting</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Passwords are encrypted using <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">bcryptjs</code> before storage:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">userSchema.pre('save', async function (next) {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (!this.isModified('password')) return next();</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const salt = await bcrypt.genSalt(10);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">this.password = await bcrypt.hash(this.password, salt);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>
</code></pre>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">7.3 JWT Token Generation</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The server generates short-lived, signed JWT tokens during successful logins:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const generateToken = (id) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return jwt.sign({ id }, process.env.JWT_SECRET, {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">expiresIn: '12h',</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">};</p>
</code></pre>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">7.4 Upload File Security</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">File uploads are managed using <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">multer</code> configured with file type and size restrictions:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const storage = multer.diskStorage({</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">destination: (req, file, cb) =&gt; cb(null, 'uploads/'),</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">filename: (req, file, cb) =&gt; cb(null, <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;"><span style="font-style:italic;">{Date.now()}-</span>{file.originalname}</code>),</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">const upload = multer({</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">storage,</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">limits: { fileSize: 5 * 1024 * 1024 }, // 5 MB max</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">fileFilter: (req, file, cb) =&gt; {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">if (file.mimetype !== 'application/pdf') {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">return cb(new Error('Only PDF documents are allowed'));</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">cb(null, true);</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">},</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">});</p>
</code></pre>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 8: System Testing &amp; Quality Assurance</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">8.1 Testing Philosophy</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Testing focused on verify core business rules, database integrity, and access controls.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">8.2 Unit Testing of Calculations</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Calculations for GPA values, attendance rates, and schedule overlaps were tested using verified mock data.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">8.3 Integration Testing</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Integration tests checked request routing, database operations, and middleware checks for typical workflows.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">8.4 Test Cases &amp; Execution Matrix</h3>

<table style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; margin:12pt 0; border:1px solid #000;"><tr style="background-color:#f8fafc;"><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Test Case ID</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Module Under Test</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Input Scenario</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Expected Output</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Status</th></tr>

<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-SEC-01</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">JWT Auth Guard</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Request without token header</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Return <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">401 Unauthorized</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-SEC-02</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Auth Role Control</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Student requests faculty <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">/grades</code> route</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Return <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">403 Forbidden</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-SCH-01</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Schedule Conflict</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Create overlapping schedule slot</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Return <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">400 Bad Request</code> room conflict</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-SCH-02</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Schedule Conflict</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Create slot starting after end time</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Return <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">400 Bad Request</code> timing error</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-ATT-01</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Attendance Registry</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Duplicate attendance entries for a course on one day</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Database rejects entry (Unique Index)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-PLC-01</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Placement Eligibility</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">CGPA = 6.9, Att = 90%, Backlogs = 0</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Eligibility = <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">false</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-PLC-02</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Placement Eligibility</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">CGPA = 8.1, Att = 72%, Backlogs = 0</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Eligibility = <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">false</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>TC-PLC-03</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Placement Eligibility</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">CGPA = 8.1, Att = 80%, Backlogs = 0</td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;">Eligibility = <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">true</code></td><td style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;"><strong>Passed</strong></td></tr>
</table>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 9: Future Scope &amp; Extensibility</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">9.1 Real-Time Notifications</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Adding WebSocket support (via Socket.io) would allow the system to send real-time notifications for timetable changes, announcements, and grade releases.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">9.2 AI-Based Performance Analysis</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Future updates could include machine learning components to analyze historical student data, helping to identify students who may need additional academic support.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">9.3 Internship Portal Integration</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Integrating an internship portal would allow companies to advertise opportunities directly to students who meet their recruitment eligibility criteria.</p>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 10: Conclusion &amp; References</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">10.1 Project Conclusion</h3>
<strong>AcadTrack</strong> provides a centralized system for managing course schedules, grades, attendance, and announcements. The application addresses the challenges of data fragmentation and manual administrative tasks by uniting these functions in a single database. Built-in tools like the Placement Eligibility Evaluator and conflict-free scheduler help students track their progress and simplify administrative scheduling.

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">10.2 References and Bibliography</h3>
