<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>ReactJS Community Guides:</strong> State Management using React Hooks and Context API. [https://react.dev/](https://react.dev/)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Express Framework Documentation:</strong> Middleware Architecture and Error Handling in Node.js. [https://expressjs.com/](https://expressjs.com/)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">4.  <strong>Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF):</strong> RFC 7519: JSON Web Tokens (JWT) Specification. [https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)</p>
